Release
LTS.398.1
of February 9, 2024
New features
The ability to view the duration of video playback in the Media widget before the video is loaded was implemented.
Table Name behavior has been changed when validating entered data when creating object types.
New features of Unread and All folders were added to GreenData Messenger.
A
legend
with developer information was added in the main menu bar.
System settings
were improved and unified: system settings are now grouped in separate instances by functional modules.
Export of Edoc documents with comments and its filtering was implemented.
Changes and improvements
Working with PDF files was improved;
Working with custom charts was improved;
Edoc: working with template editor was improved, working with bookmarks was stabilized, bookmark version comparison was improved;
Working with role_admin, all_users access groups was improved;
Automatic filling of the table name of the File object attribute was improved;
Working with the Light registry was improved: display of custom actions, button operation and drop-down lists was stabilized;
Display of table heights when switching to visual editing was stabilized;
Column width changes in the dashboard were stabilized;
Charts downloading in the dashboard was stabilized;
Working with onChange algorithm call was stabilized: read-only attributes are now removed;
Working with the kanban board tasks was stabilized;
Anonymous authorization was stabilized;
Display of sub-steps in the advanced status bar was stabilized;
Algorithm editor operation was stabilized;
Printed Forms file saving was stabilized;
File preview in the registry was stabilized;
Working with guf was improved: the system displays a warning message when an object is not found on the instance.
